title: Girls Just Want To Have Fun (Sarah Jessica Parker/Helen Hunt)
description:
A younger [b]Sarah Jessica Parker [/b] and [b]Helen Hunt [/b] (the best friend) star in this charming romantic movie, for all the family, about a high-school girl ([b]Parker[/b]) who wants to enter a dance competition but finds that she needs a partner.  Meet Drew ([b]Lee Montgomery[/b]) who could be either the her knight in shining armour or the boy of her nightmares, he only wants to dance but his family aren&#039;t too happy about his ambitions, they want him to settle down to a normal steady job.  Could both dancers prove to their families and themselves that they are becoming what they were born to be or will it all end in disaster? 

NOT A PORN MOVIE!!!
